  "prompt": "Is there a way to tell if someone in Skype is currently in a call or messaging someone?",
  "response": "Yes, Skype provides visual cues to indicate a user's current activity, including whether they are in a call or actively messaging. Here's how you can tell:\n\n**1. Status Indicators:**\n\n*   **Green checkmark in a circle:** This means the person is available and not currently in a call or active messaging.\n\n*   **Yellow clock:** This means the person is away.\n\n*   **Red Do Not Disturb:** This means the person is set as busy and doesn't want to be disturbed.\n\n*   **A ringing animation or a phone icon:** Indicates that the person is currently in a call.\n    *   **A camera icon** Indicates that the person is currently in a video call.\n\n*   **Solid Green Dot with Typing Animation:** If the person is actively typing in a chat window, you'll typically see a solid green dot along with an animation indicating they are typing next to their name.\n\n**2. Within the Chat Window:**\n\n*   **\"They are in a call\" or \"On a call\":**  Skype will often explicitly state this in the chat window if the person is actively in a call.  You might see this near their name at the top of the chat.\n\n**Important Considerations and Limitations:**\n\n*   **Status Can Be Manually Set:** Users can manually set their status to Away, Do Not Disturb, or Invisible. This means their displayed status might not accurately reflect their actual activity.\n*   **Invisible Status:** If someone sets their status to \"Invisible,\" you won't be able to see their actual status. They will always appear offline to you.\n*   **Delay:** There can sometimes be a slight delay in status updates.\n*   **Mobile App:** The indicators are generally the same on the Skype mobile app, but layout may vary slightly.\n*   **Not a Guarantee:** Even with these indicators, you can't be 100% certain of someone's activity.  They might be in a call on another device or using a different platform.\n\n**In summary, pay attention to the status indicators next to their name in your contact list and within the chat window itself. These are the best indicators of their current activity on Skype.**\n",
